description: Daily newspaper in Gainesville, Georgia, U.S.
label: The Gainesville Times
title: The_Gainesville_Times_(Georgia)
exrest: The Gainesville Times is a daily newspaper based in Gainesville, Georgia, that covers Hall County and Northeast Georgia. As of 2019, the general manager is Norman Baggs and the editor in chief is Shannon Casas; headquarters are located at 345 Green Street, NW Gainesville, GA 30501.
